  <brief_title>Maintenance of Vitamin D Level by UVB Radiation</brief_title>
  <official_title>How Much UVB Radiation is Necessary to Maintain Summer Vitamin D Level During Winter?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
